<h3>Our Story</h3>
<p class="text-justify">
   Pizza Express was the first organization to bring up the idea of in house production of Pizza in Willington, New Zealand in 1999. Since Inception, our constant emphasis on quality consciousness and innovating with new recepies has delighted the taste buds of many customers. Our presence in Willington,New Zealand has been adding wholesome goodness to the lives of thousands since decade.
    Since its launch in 1999, we are growing as a manufacturer as well as a supplier. We are equipped with all sort of modern and high – tech machineries to ensure a high standard production.  We have our own fully functional supply unit to support timely stock delivery. In a span of only few years, our family has grown by 50 District Dealers, increased number of delivery boys, satisfied company employees and thousands of retailer counters.
</p>
<h3>
    Our Vision
</h3>
<p  class="text-justify">
    To make Pizza Express the first choice of the customers of all ages, by setting high standards in taste, quality, service delivery and price.
    We believe in producing and selling pizza that are healthy for human consumption, in a manner that demonstrates greatest concern for health & safety of all life forms and for safety and sustainability of nature and our environment.

</p>
<h3>
    Our Mission
</h3>
<p class="text-justify">
    Our mission is to uphold the highest level of integrity in all we do, from the quality and origin of our food to our care for the health of our customers and the environment.
</p>
